before_text:
## Sandbox SDK - writeFiles

```javascript
sandbox.writeFiles([
  { path: 'run.sh', content: '#!/bin/bash\necho "ready"' }
]);
```

Note: To make files executable, use a separate chmod call after writing.

after_text:
## Sandbox SDK - writeFiles

```javascript
sandbox.writeFiles([
  { path: 'run.sh', content: '#!/bin/bash\necho "ready"', mode: 0o755 }
]);
```

The optional `mode` property sets file permissions directly, eliminating the need for a separate chmod call.

